Author: BEDBulimic
Text: We don't provide tips to lose weight here (rule #1) and we're hesitant to talk numbers here. This sub is largely for emotional support, so you can vent about how you feel and try to help you feel happy with your body, but no one is going to tell you how to lose weight.
